node.text: CB being lifted In context is like u are free to go but u can’t go freely

Singapore’s “circuit breaker” will finally lift on Jun 1, but it will be gradually done in three phases. Here’s what activities will resume (and what you’ll have to wait a little longer for) during Phase 1. Check out the full video on our IGTV for Phases 2 and 3 – and don’t forget to bookmark this page and share with friends and family. #Singapore #circuitbreaker (Art: Rafa Estrada)
